::DarkMouse::

She smiled. "I landed in a stasis pod.  I was sent on a scientific mission 
of exploration. To find resourced and other sources of energy. But the ship 
ran into an astoroid field and fell apart.  I landed here.  No one else on 
the ship made it that I know of.  I think I was the only one to escape in 
time before the ship exploded in space.  It was the rough landing that 
jarred my circiuts."
She sighed, "That's why I changed sides for a little while. My circiuts got 
messed up.  But I'm glad you fixed my programming."
She smiled and hugged him. She liked being so close to him.
